her, dass das Simulations-Framework auf logisch-mathematischer Integrität beruht.</p><h3 data-path-to-node="13">1. Erweiterte Axiome &amp; Epistemische Transparenz</h3><p data-path-to-node="14">Um systemische Halluzinationen zu eliminieren, wird jede fundamentale Annahme im System mit einer Konfidenzwahrscheinlichkeit <span class="math-inline" data-math="P" data-index-in-node="126"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.6833em;"></span><span style="margin-right: 0.1389em;" class="mord mathnormal">P</span></span></span></span></span>, dem Gültigkeitsbereich <span class="math-inline" data-math="B" data-index-in-node="152"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.6833em;"></span><span style="margin-right: 0.0502em;" class="mord mathnormal">B</span></span></span></span></span> und der Quelle <span class="math-inline" data-math="Q" data-index-in-node="169"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.8778em; vertical-align: -0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">Q</span></span></span></span></span> versehen.</p><ul data-path-to-node="15"><li><p data-path-to-node="15,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="15,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Existenzaxiom:</b> <span class="math-inline" data-math="\exists x : x \in U" data-index-in-node="15"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.6944em;"></span><span class="mord">∃</span><span class="mord mathnormal">x</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">:</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.5782em; vertical-align: -0.0391em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">x</span><span class="mspace" style